results.content: This is an excellent course which I highly recommend to anyone who is interested in an overview of the development of web applications. It is only a short course that only teaches theory. However, it provides the context that will help you understand other courses that focus on the details of the various components needed for a web application. Great work Sanjay. I'm looking forward to your other courses.
